  "title": "All-Party Parliamentary Group on Carers",
  "purpose": "To ensure the millions of people in the UK providing unpaid care for family and friends get the support they need. The Group brings together parliamentarians on a cross-party basis to promote awareness, share knowledge, and better understand of the needs of unpaid carers.",
